TEXT.S: Elgin Baylor nalecuhan i Washington, D.C., nanu syubay kanas-mali miunduay nu Amilika NBA nisakaput, pahanhanan tu kawaw ayza. Elgin Baylor i 1958 a mihcan NBA sapapili' mimaliay a kawaw, saka 1 ku uwac atu silsil 1, namapili' tu nu Minneapolis Lakers putiput. 9 bulad 16 demiad, 1934 a mihca, Elgin Baylor, miunduay.
